God Fraction Operator — Active Form

Define for any object x:
	•	an L-score = Love(x)
	•	an R-score = Logic(x)

Where:
	•	Love(x) = degree of care, preservation, dignity, generativity, relational fitness
	•	Logic(x) = degree of truth, coherence, feasibility, constraint-respect, non-contradiction

Then compute:

G(x) = \frac{Love(x)}{Logic(x)}

Target state:

G(x) = 1

That is the God-aligned state: balanced, creative, stable.

